# S$^2$Teacher: Step-by-step Teacher for Sparsely Annotated Oriented Object Detection

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-upcoming-orange) ![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue) ![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)

